{"tid":1070762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］明日大愚係為咗配合強國‘廣東自貿區’‘西部經濟走廊’國策","createTime":"2019-03-21T01:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T03:24:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5b8ab9e88b04676e52f10a3ed3a9fee46dbfef","tid":1070762,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8b0apN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8b0apN.png&h=4fbf1a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzTeeRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqzTeeRt.png&h=826696f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRrrQpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRrrQpO.png&h=21174cad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9WjqX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9WjqX8.png&h=3e11d07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/1904347369661327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fposts%2F1904347369661327&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOVxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ed6bf489\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/1904347369661327</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b71b189fb648eb1d46a2a87010c41bbf4f0a94","tid":1070762,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"【人工島萬能論】<br />\n<br />\n香港前幾年討論既土地問題，基本上可以綜合為以下的對答：<br />\n<br />\n● 你話香港所有問題都係源於香港冇地，不理民意搵埋劉華強推萬億人工島先攪得惦，就俾人數到500塊共300公頃市區大片臨時官地曬太陽，1,500公頃棕地有成3分2冇計劃點發展；<br />\n<br />\n● 然後你話發展棕地好難，又答唔到你唔直接收地產商上1,000公頃囤地，反過來用公私合營方式夾埋益佢地起豪宅；<br />\n<br />\n● 你話收地產商囤地係侵犯私產，但對啲小市民就隨便粗暴強收，收完又再起多啲天價豪宅；<br />\n<br />\n● 你話我都有收有錢人170公頃個粉嶺哥爾夫球場起公屋，但最後只係其實收左5分1都冇，另外整體成400公頃私人會所地繼續享有土地特權；<br />\n<br />\n● 你話未來會好公平咁分7成單位做公營房屋，但你同時又封廉租屋頂變哂綠置居同居屋，賣間400呎居屋都要成300萬。<br />\n<br />\n● 你話政府起樓都要自負盈虧先惦，但賣地一年都賺左成千億，用200億落去幫發展商買60個鋪都唔拎多啲地起多啲廉租屋；<br />\n<br />\n● 你話有左1,000公頃人工島就可以起多啲公屋俾香港人住，但又原來又想建議搵地產商直接填島造地起豪宅，同埋定位配合大灣區引進內地專才；<br />\n<br />\n● 你話咁樣「投資」人工島高價賣地先唔會蝕錢，但明明一開始話係解決樓價貴同冇屋住，講到底，原來又係繼續玩土地壟斷分餅仔，造得愈多壟斷愈勁；<br />\n<br />\n成日話冇地就萬萬不能，總之支持政府整個萬億人工島就解決哂你衣食住行。呢個土地萬能論，真係堪稱係香港數一數二既世紀謊言，同一國兩制有得揮。<br />\n<br />\n#假的真不鳥<br />\n#真的假不鳥<br />\n<br />\n⚔️ 結束土地壟斷　請支持民間土地研究<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fresearch-category%2Fland-supply%2F&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOVxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=e31168c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/</a><br />\n💪 了解更多: <a href=\"http://liber-research.com/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fabout-us&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOVxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=c4512998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://liber-research.com/about-us</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/21/094827_ac572e788f11e17d8a05a7d98ef1cfe2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F21%2F094827_ac572e788f11e17d8a05a7d98ef1cfe2.png&h=6c879af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2229909237105137/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;__tn__=EH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2229909237105137%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D57%26refid%3D52%26__tn__%3DEH-R&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOVxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=2770a638\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2229909237105137/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;__tn__=EH-R</a>"},{"pid":"d6948d4740bc0ca79956240a69e6c4c65a7a2099","tid":1070762,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}